184
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,280
Caledon, bought his fiancee.

185
00:16:25,700 --> 00:16:26,700
You.

186
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:29,370
A week before he sailed on Titanic.

187
00:16:30,370 --> 00:16:32,700
