199
00:17:32,770 --> 00:17:35,430
Are you ready to go back to Titanic?

200
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:40,190
Okay, here we go.

201
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:43,480
She hits the berg on the starboard side, right?

202
00:17:43,570 --> 00:17:44,570
