217
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,430
So, what happens?

218
00:18:16,890 --> 00:18:18,600
She splits, right down to the keel.

219
00:18:18,690 --> 00:18:19,690
And the stern...

220
00:18:20,150 --> 00:18:21,150
