1978
02:50:32,850 --> 02:50:34,520
Warm in her bed.

1979
02:50:36,190 --> 02:50:37,310
Not here.

1980
02:50:38,190 --> 02:50:40,690
Not this night. Not like this.

1981
02:50:41,030 --> 02:50:42,690
Do you understand me?

